      <title>股市动荡，债券价格在选举和美联储加息中上涨：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-03/dollar-weakens-as-us-polls-signal-no-clear-leader-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着债券价格上涨，股票价格难以获得提振，在美联储做出决定之前，民意调查继续显示美国总统大选竞争激烈。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-03/dollar-weakens-as-us-polls-signal-no-clear-leader-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 03 Nov 2024 22:45:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>摩尔多瓦领导人赢得选举 重启欧盟加入之路</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-03/moldova-s-pro-eu-president-headed-for-victory-in-key-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩尔多瓦总统玛雅·桑杜周日在前苏联加盟共和国的选举中取得决定性胜利，无视俄罗斯干扰选举的努力，并重新推动该国在 2020 年前加入欧盟。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-03/moldova-s-pro-eu-president-headed-for-victory-in-key-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 03 Nov 2024 21:25:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>交易员们为漫长而动荡的选举之夜做准备</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2024-11-03/how-traders-are-preparing-to-watch-2024-election-night-results</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着结果陆续公布，一些精神高度集中的投资者将密切关注利润率，并调整他们的赌注，直到日出为止。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2024-11-03/how-traders-are-preparing-to-watch-2024-election-night-results</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 03 Nov 2024 20:00:27 GMT</pubDate>
